meaningMnemonic: Time to <kanji>overcome</kanji> the <kanji>clothes</kanji> of our enemies. They all wear the same kind of clothes (let's say blue clothes) so we know that if we overcome the blue coated people, we will have won. It will be a <vocabulary>conquest</vocabulary>!
